data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail
data.value: Man kojkowin taj kaqaya' b'e che le k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik. Qas chawila' we utz ri q'alajisanem on chakojo' jun chi k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik. We k'a kak'am na we oqxa'n, che'ach'ab'ej le ja k'olme'r.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail2
data.value: Xriqitaj jun k'axk'olil are taq kab'an le chakub'al rech tojonem. Chach'ab'ej le kempatanel chech uriqik tob'anem.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails. Probably, the PI is rejected by risk.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.BR
data.value: We uq'axexik man kakowinb'ex ta uya'ik b'e chech. Chab'ana' jun toq'ob', chak'amb'ejaj le aq'alajisanem. Wene' jujun taq kemuwujil rech tojonik man kek'am taj xa pa we ub'antajik tojonik, kuqxa'nixik kakoj jun kemuwujil rech tojonik. We kuya' na le k'eyowal, chach'ab'ej apan le aja k'olpwaq.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Brazil. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.MX
data.value: We uq'axexik man kakowinb'ex ta uya'ik b'e chech. Chab'ana' jun toq'ob', chak'amb'ejaj le aq'alajisanem. Wene' jujun taq kemuwujil rech tojonik man kek'am taj xa rumal le ub'antajik tojonik xa rumal le taqanem rech chajinem pa le uk'olib'al. We kuya' na le k'eyowal, chach'ab'ej apan le aja k'olpwaq.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Mexico. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.CardUsedMuiltipleTimes

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.AR
data.value:
Chech utzujuxik k'ayij chi'l taq Patanib'al, rajawaxik kawinaqirisaj jun akemb'i'aj. Amaq'el are taq kaya' jun k'ak' chakub'al rech tojonik chech jun k'ayij on jun patanib'al, wene' kak'utun le jun b'ixikil chi'l kaqata chi awech we kaya' b'e mojo'qa qataqej chi jumul. Are taq kawinaqirisax le kemb'i'aj on le kik'exsuk'maxik taq k'ak' chakub'al rech tojonik. Are chi we taq q'axenem qas ketz'aqatik, kata q'alajisanem rech winaqil pacha': Le ab'i', kemriqonib'al, rajilab'al sik'ib'al, kemriqonib'al rech taqoqxa'n rajilab'alil uwujil qajanik chi'l rajilab'alil kemb'i'aj rech ja k'olpwaq. Xuquje' wene' kamulix le kemriqonib'al IP chi'l le q'alajisanel wiqkemchakub'al xuquje' ke'akixim we juq'attzij ruk' le q'alajisanem winaqil chech uwinaqirisaxik jun kemb'i'aj on pa le uk'exsuk'maxik jun k'ak' chakub'al rech tojonik.
IQas kinya' b'e che Microsoft corporation, chi kech le e raqan uq'ab' chi'l le kiximom kib' ruk' che ukojik le q'alajisanem winaqil le ya'talik che uwinaqirisaxik le ya'tal pa le wujil pacha' le kariqitaj pa le cholajil 5 chi'l pa le taqanikwuj 25326 are chi kataq la chi wech le taq wuj kajab'uxik rech rajil k'ayij, echeb'alil on patanib'al. Kinq'alajisaj chi pacha' le kub'ij pa le q'ataj 6 rech le taqantz'ib'am 25326 ya'om uq'alajisanem le ub'antajik uya'ik b'e.
We man kaya' ta le q'alajisanem winaqil, le uk'axk'olil are le man kakowimb'ex ta uriqik le k'ayij chi'l le taq patanib'al le ya'tal pa we uxaq web'. Are taq kinya' le nuq'alajisanem winaqil kinya' b'e che uk'olik pa le mulib'al juq'attzij rech Microsoft Corporation, K'aywokaj rech Redmod,WA 98052 (EE.UU.). Le rajaw le q'alajisanem winaqil utz kuya' b'e che uriqik wa' pa sipatalik pa unajal wene' waqib' ik' (Xew we k'o wujil che uqasaxik uq'ijol pacha' le kub'ij pa le ralcholajil 3 rech le cholajil 14 rech le taqantz'ib'am 25326). Le taqanel ri k'o pa ukab' rilik le ukojik le taqantz'ib' 25326 are DIRECCIÓN DE PROTECCIÓN DE DATOS PERSONALES DE ARGENTINA. k'o pa raqan uq'ab' che rilik le uch'o'jixik we man utz ta uchajixik le q'alajisanem winaqil kab'anik taqanik.
Utz katok chi upam le aq'alajisanem winaqil chi'l utz kab'an k'exonem pa le kemb'i'aj https://commerce.microsoft.com. We kawaj kak'ex le aq'alajisanem winaqil, pa le wujil katajin k'u kaya' b'e la' chech Microsoft Corporation che umulixik chi'l uk'olik pacha' le tz'ib'an kanoq.
Chech uwinaqirisaxik jun kemb'i'aj chi'l upitz'ik pa le pitz'b'al "Kink'amo" le teren chi loq, kaya' b'e chech Microsoft Corporation le aq'alajisanem winaqil, chi'l kaya' b'e are chi Microsoft Corporation kumulij, chi'l kuq'axej, are tzij jas kub'ij pa le wujil.
data.comment: Consent text for ES-AR

We jun q'alajisanem rech kemb'i'aj rech q'alajisanem winaqil kamulixik k'ate k'u ri' kaq'axex pa aninaqil, pa chajinem chi'l pa uq'atexik uwach, chech Microsoft corporation pa Estados Unidos are chi kab'an le uq'axexik le tz'onotalik chi'l uya'ik le k'ayij chi'l patanib'al. data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.KR
data.value:
We q'alajisanem rech k'utwinaqil kemb'i'aj kariqitajik xuquje' kataq b'i aninaq pa Microsoft Corporation pa Estados Unidos are taq kawinaqirisax le kemb'i'aj pa ub'antajik qas utz xuquje' nitz'arisam chech ub'anik taq q'axenem. Le juq'atttzij ri' utz kekojik xuquje' keq'atex k'a 12 junab' pa le uk'isb'al atojonem. Utz kach'aw apan pa Microsoft Corporation chi rij uchakuxik le q'alajisanem rech ajch'ab'e'n pa le Uq'alajisaxik le recheb'alil Microsoft pa nimk'atz k'o waral: http://privacy.microsoft.com/ko-kr.
Microsoft kakowinik kukomonej le aq'alajisanem rech winaqilal kuk' nik'aj chik, chi'l xa k'u man ruk' ta uq'atexik pa CyberSource Corp.,Receivable Management Services and Inicis. Le aq'alajisanem kataq b'i are taq rajawaxik uq'axexik, chech ub'anik taq q'axnem rech q'atb'al tzij, uk'ulaxik uwach taq ya'om ub'ixik, uq'atik le elaq' on ruk' ub'anik rech ujunamaxik.
Katkowinik on kak'exsuk'umaj aq'alajisanem winaqilal pa: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Wene' kawaj kak'exsuk'umaj le aq'alajisanem, xa jewa' katajin kaya' b'e chech Microsoft Corporation chech uriqik xuquje' uq'axexik aninaq le aq'alajisanem winaqilal jas ya'om ub'ixik ajsik.
Are taq kawinaqirisaj jun kemb'i'aj xuquje' upitz'ik pa le pitz'b'al 'Agree' chi uxe', kaya' b'e chech Microsoft Corporation ruk' le aq'alajisanem winaqilal xuquje' le aya'b'al b'e are chi Microsoft kuriqo, kuq'axej xuquje' kukomonej le aq'alajisanem k'utwinaqilal kuk' nik'aj chik jas ya'om ub'ixik waral xuquje' pa le Uq'alajisaxik recheb'alil Microsoft pa nimk'atz chi utz kariq waral: http://privacy.microsoft.com/ko-kr
data.comment: Consent text for KO-KR!

data.name: Literal.PICVC.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Kaya pa le awujil jun tojonik man q'alajisam taj kumajij pa {1} xuquje' {2} {0}.
  • Le tojonik ya'om katoq'ixik we xtz'aqat le q'axnem rech uk'amb'ejaxik.
  • Chech uk'amb'ejaxik, rajawaxik kaq'alajisaj le tojonik ya'om, ON le retal oxib' ajilab'al ya'om pa le uq'alajisaxik uq'axexik pwaq.
  • Chech reta'maxik le tojonik ya'om on le retal oxib' ajilab'al, chwila' le uq'alajisab'al uwujil. We tz'onoj utz kab'an, pa nimk'atz, pa sik'ib'al on pa le uq'alajisab'al taqoqxa'n, are tzij le upataninem le ja k'olpwaq.
  • Rajawaxik katz'aqatisaj we uk'amb'ejaxik nab'e chech{3}; karaj na {4} ub'anik.
  • Are tzij jawi' at k'o wi xuquje' jawi' k'o wi le ja k'olpwaq le kayo'w le uwujil, wene' le ja' k'olpwaq kut'a jun tojonik rech uq'axexik pwaq pa k'i taq ti (ITF) on jun tojonik rumal uk'exik taq pwaq pa le tojonik ya'om are taq xb'an le q'axnem rech uk'amb'ejaxik. Are chi kawe'tamaj we kab'an we tojonik, chata pa le ja k'olpwaq kayo'w le uwujil. Microsoft man kutzalijisaj ta le tojonik rech ITF on rech uk'exik taq pwaq le kakoj chech uk'amb'ejaxik.
data.comment: PICVC term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.PICVD.Input.Inform
data.value: Xb'an uq'axexik pwaq rech uk'ab'ejaxik pa le akemb'iaj rech ja k'olpwaq. chata' le chi ronojel xuquje' kemtz'ib'aj le pwaq kaya pa le akemb'iaj rech ja k'olpwaq on kemtz'ib'aj le retal 3 ajilab'al le kariqitaj pa le uq'alajisanem rech le uq'axexik pwaq.

data.name: Literal.PICVD.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Kaya' pa le akemb'i'aj rech ja k'olpwaq jun tojonik man q'alajisam taj chi uxo'l {0} {1} - {2} pa le akemb'i'aj rech jak'olpwaq.
  • Chech uk'amb'ejaxik, rajawaxik kaq'alajisaj le tojonik ya'om, on le retal rech 3 ajilab'al ya'om pa le ucholajixik le uq'axexik pwaq.
  • Chech uriqik le tojonik ya'om chi'l le retal 3 ajilab'al, chawila' le akemb'iaj rech jak'olpwaq. Are tzij le patanib'al rech le ajak'olpwaq, wa' pa nimk'atz kb'an wi, pa ch'aweb'al on pa uwujil loq'oj le kul pa taqoqxán.
  • Rajawaxik katz'aqatisaj ub'anik wa' nab'e {3} xuquje' wene {4} chech ub'anik chi jumul.
data.comment: PICVD term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.PICVCDDPayin.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Kaqaya' na nik'aj rajil man q'alajisam taj wene' {1} - {2} {0} pa le akemb'i'aj rech ja k'olpwaq.
  • Le rajil ya'om katzalijisax na we xtz'aqat apan le q'axnem rech uk'amb'ejaxik.
  • Are chi utz kub'an le uk'amb'ejaxik, rajawaxik katz'ib'aj jampa le rajilab'alil ya'om, ON LE retal oxib' ajilab'al ya'om pa le ucholajixik le uq'axeb'al pwaq.
  • Kariq janipa le rajil ya'om xuquje' le retal oxib' ajilab'al pa le uq'alajisab'al le kemb'i'aj rech ja k'olpwaq. Are tzij le pataninem kuya' le ja k'olpwaq, wene' utz kata we q'alajisanem pa nimk'atz, pa sik'ib'al on pa le wuj rech le taqoqxa'n.
  • Rajawaxik katz'aqatisaj we k'amb'ejanem mojo'qa chech {3}; karaj na {4} ub'anik.
  • Are tzij jawi at k'o wi xuquje' le ja k'olpwaq, wene' le ja k'olpwaq kutoq'ij jun q'atoj tojonik rech uq'axexik pwaq pa k'i taq tinamit (ITF) on kuta rajil rumal uk'exik uwach taq rajil pa le uk'iyal ya'om are taq xb'an le q'axnem rech uk'amb'ejaxik. Are chi kaweta'maj we kab'an we tojonik, chata' pa le ja' k'olpwaq jawi' ko wi le akemb'i'aj. Microsoft MAN kutzalijisaj ta le q'atoj tojonik ITF xuquje' le tojonik rech uq'axexik taq pwaq le kakoj pa we q'axnem rech uk'amb'ejaxik.
data.comment: PICVC DDPayin term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.Error.PolicyReject
data.value: Man kojkowin taj kaq'ak'am taq wujil nab'e tojonik. Chacha' jun chik k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik.
data.comment: The error message for RIME_PrePaid_List_POLICY_REJECT from RISK team.

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsg
data.value: Rumal jun k'axk'olil ruk' le ujeqeb'axik ActiveX, le e rajaw le kakikoj taq kemnik'onel web le man are ta IE (Internet Explorer) man kekowin taj kakib'an kemtz'ib'axik kib' pa le k'ak taq patanib'al rech Azure. Chech ub'anik, chakojo' IE. Are taq le k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik xkemtz'ib'atajik, katkowinik kakoj taq patanib'al rech Azure ruk' nik'aj chik kemnikonel web. Chakuyu' qamak.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsgActiveX
data.value: Ruk' uq'alajisaxik chi le okib'al rech tojonem petinaq chech ActiveX, we katajin kakoj nik'aj chi nik'onelab' (chi'l Microsoft Edge) chi man are' ta Internet Explorer, man kakowinb'ex ta ub'anik le uk'asunem Azure. Chab'ana' jun toq'ob' chakojo' Internet Explorer chech utz'ib'axik, utz kakoj apachike nik'onel. Kuyu' chech le katajin kak'ulmatajik.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.NameMsg
data.value: Chab'ana' jun toq'ob' chatz'ib'aj le ab'i' pa inglés are chi qas utz kawil pa taq le uwujil.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Authorization.WarningMsg
data.value: Wene' kawil jun q'atenem k'o uq'ijol pa le kemtaqanik rech le awujil. Man kab'an ta jun tojonem pa le awujil.
data.comment: Added to warn customers about authorization charges.

data.name: Literal.Authorization.Azure.WarningMsg
data.value: Le kemawujil man kaya' taj, pine' utz kawil le uya'ik b'e xa k'o uq'ijol q'atem.
data.comment: Added to warn customers about authorization charges.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthorizationFail
data.value: Man kakowinb'ex ta uya'ik b'e chech le ub'anik tojonem. We kataq na we oqxa'n chi awech, chab'ana' ruk' jun chi ub'anik tojonem on chach'ab'ej le patanib'al loq'ob'anel chech uriqik tob'anem.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails for internal reasons.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAccountName
data.value: Ub'i' le rajaw le kemb'i'aj man utz taj. Chatz'ib'aj jun q'alajisanem qas utz.
data.comment: The error message shown when account name is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidCountry
data.value: Chaya' jun q'alajisanem rech tinamit chi qas utz.
data.comment: The error message shown when country is invalid.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.Header
data.value: Chak'ak'arisaj taq nab'e ya'talil rech tojonik

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.SubHeader
data.value: Chanim utz chik kakoj le ya'b'al b'e rech taq tojonik rech Microsoft ruk' nab'e ya'b'al b'e, we k'o PayPal are taq katoj pa Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.US
data.value: Chakojo PayPal chech taq tojonik aq'anoq pa le wokk'olib'al rech Microsoft. We k'o na ame'r pa PayPal are la' nab'e kkojik, pene' achom jun ajawatal k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik. We man acha'om ta jun ajawatal k'amb'al cholajil, kkoj le k'amb'al cholajl rech tojonik le ya'om chi uloq. We q'axinaq chi uq'ijol on xk'is le ajawatal k'amb'al cholajil on le ya'om chi uloq, le PayPal kuya' le k'amb'al ucholajil rech k'oltob'anel. Utz kajeqeb'a' on kak'ex le k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonik. on kaq'atej we ya'talil pa apachike uq'ijol pa taq asuk'manem pa PayPal.com. K'a te' we kaya' jun k'amb'al cholajil rech tojonem, le k'amb'al cholajil le kojom kuterene'j rij taq taqanem rech tojonem pa PayPal.com.
data.comment: Text for United States, Canada, Brazil

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.DE
data.value: Kak'am uq'ab chi Microsoft utz kutaq taq taqanem rech tojonik rech PayPal suk'um pa Microsoft chech Microsoft chi'l chi kech taq q'alajisatal k'ulunelab' rech tojonik le kkikoj le wokk'olib'al rech Microsoft. Ri at kaya' b'e chech PayPal kukomone'j le ucholajil taq uq'axexik pwaq rech PayPal rech Microsoft, rachi'l le q'alajisanem le amaq'el kkomone'x ruk' jun k'ulunel rech taq tojonik are tzij le uchomab'al recheb'alil. Wa' kuya' b'e chech Microsoft krilo we utz xub'an le atojonik xuquje' katu'o' chech ub'anik le uq'axexik pwaq. PayPal utz kub'ij chech Microsoft we krelesaj le ya'talil. Kuya' taqanem chech PayPal are chi kril le taq tz'onoj rech tojonik taqom rumal Microsoft are tzij we kuya' b'e chech. We k'o na ame'r rech PayPal are kkoj nab'e, We kq'atexik on kk'is le upetib'al me'r ya ya'om chi uloq, kqoq'ix le k'oltob'anel. Utz kaq'atab'a we ya'talil on kak'ex le ajawatal upetb'al pwaqilal apachike uq'ijol pa le akemb'i'aj rech PayPal. We katoj pa jun pwaqilal le man are ta uk'u'x pwaqilal rech le akemb'i'aj rech Paypal, le PayPal kuk'ex le pwaqilal pa le rajilal rech kamik.
data.comment: Text for Germany, Netherlands, Sweden, United Kingdom, Russia

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: Jawi' kchokon wi, le loq'omanelab' rech EU rajawaxik kkiya' taq ucholajil ajilab'al on rech utz'ib'axik ib' rech utz IVA. We man kb'an taj wene kuk'ex le ub'anik IVA rech le uwujil loq'oj ya'om rumal Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.EG.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: Where applicable, Egypt customers should provide details of their valid VAT registration number. Failure to do so may impact upon the VAT treatment of the invoice issued by Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line1
data.value: Le q'aqtoj tojonik rech taq echeb'alil chi'l taq pataninem rech Nueva Zelandia (NZ GST) pa 15% kkoj chech najatarisam taq pataninem pa k'ulamaq' chi'l man kb'an ta uk'exik ya'om kumal taq k'ayinelab' le man ajwaralik taj chech jun waralik winaq pa Nueva Zelanda, xew we le winaq are jun tz'ib'atal k'aywokaj pa GST. Jun k'ayinel rajawaxik kuchomaj chi le le k'ulunel man tz'ib'atal taj, xew we le k'ulunel kuya' ub'ixik le k'ayinel chi ri are' utz'ib'am rib' chi'l kuya' le rajilab'alil tz'ib'an ib' rech NZ GST.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line2
data.value: Pa we t'iqonem, chaya' le rajilab'alil utz'ib'axik ib' rech NZ GST rech le acholwokaj. We man je ta la', le NZ GST chech 15% wene kya pa le ya'talil chi awech.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line3

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.BR.Line1
